name: Vintage Beaded Top - So Right Now
description: This awesome black, ivory, silver, and gold vintage top is covered in bugle beads, sequins, and metallic stitching. V-neck in front and back, with zigzag edging, and side slits. I cannot find a label but I believe this top will fit a a size small best. It measures 32" in the bust and is in a pull-on style. Great for holiday season - and I can pretty much guarantee you won't run into anyone else in the same top!

name: Jaymee Luu Handmade Earrings with Cameos and Roses
description: A pretty bead sparkles in the center of the roses, and a black cameo is framed against a copper shield. Definitely a dark, romantic and Victorian  vibe about these. Measure just over an inch.

name: Handmade Jaymee Luu Necklace with Vintage Charms
description: Regular Closet Space customers will remember when we carried jewelry designer Jaymee Luu's pieces in the shop. Always handmade, with new and vintage charms, and always sold out. Here is another sweet necklace of her's with blue tourmaline, a tiny round rose-covered locket (yes, it opens), a twig, the world's smallest harmonica, and a faceted white bead. 16". Love it.

name: New Shari Dixon Necklace on Red Suede with Stones
description: Handmade Shari Dixon 15" necklace with a clustering of shell and semi-precious stone drops hanging from a red suede cord. The red makes it  fun for holiday, and would be dramatic with a black dresss. But this necklace is also all-year-round pretty, and would be equally stunning with a white blouse.

name: 16" Vintage Necklace with Horse Charm. Giddy-up!
description: If you are a horse-lover AND a hip girl, this enamel horse head necklace is for you. It's small (but not too small; head measures just under an inch) but is big in the cool quotient. And, the simple and classic goldtone chain adds just the right amount of old-school.
